"{\"uid\": \"blueprint.ng-paris-olympics-britain-clinch-historic-gold-in-womens-quadruple-sculls\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"August 1, 2024Admin IIISports0  Great Britain's rowers won Olympic gold in a dramatic end to the women's quadruple sculls after a photo finish with the Netherlands.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 164, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 32, \"end\": 45, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_women's_national_field_hockey_team\", \"score\": 0.999948580997222, \"rank\": 3.9986336177055655e-05, \"text\": \"Great Britain\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_women's_national_field_hockey_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_women's_national_field_hockey_team\"}, {\"begin\": 152, \"end\": 163, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"score\": 0.9047066110638147, \"rank\": 0.09937527939431676, \"text\": \"Netherlands\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Dutch led from the front and were half a boat length clear with 200m to go in Paris before an astonishing push from GB pipped them at the line.\", \"from\": 166, \"to\": 313, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 170, \"end\": 175, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"score\": 0.9352379949858871, \"rank\": 0.04865616938394957, \"text\": \"Dutch\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\"}, {\"begin\": 248, \"end\": 253, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999996548468, \"rank\": 3.4492787156995203e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 286, \"end\": 288, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9042