dbpedia.org/resource/Tyler_Anderson\", \"score\": 0.8552962380430578, \"rank\": 0.1691844758405225, \"text\": \"Anderson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tyler_Anderson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tyler_Anderson\"}, {\"begin\": 1378, \"end\": 1382, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lola_Cars\", \"score\": 0.9999701026285134, \"rank\": 2.8420557635959614e-05, \"text\": \"Lola\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lola_Cars\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lola_Cars\"}, {\"begin\": 1383, \"end\": 1391, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tyler_Anderson\", \"score\": 0.8552962380430578, \"rank\": 0.1691844758405225, \"text\": \"Anderson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tyler_Anderson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tyler_Anderson\"}, {\"begin\": 1504, \"end\": 1506, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9042578916784302, \"rank\": 0.10587920680833945, \"text\": \"GB\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And then, she threw it away.\", \"from\": 1509, \"to\": 1537, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Without her knowledge, her father retrieved it and kept it for seven years and, having been diagnosed with terminal cancer,he wanted to remind her of her dreams.\", \"from\": 1539, \"to\": 1700, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I know that he would be so proud of me,\\\" a teary Anderson said after receiving her medal.\", \"from\": 1702, \"to\": 1792, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1752, \"end\": 1760, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tyler_Anderson\", \"score\": 0.8552962380430578, \"rank\": 0.1691844758405225, \"text\": \"And